            <span id="Second_Paragraph_Mod">
                I got baptized. The baptism was amazing. I did not know how to swim and was afraid of water, and I didn’t think I could survive this baptism ceremony. But when I went under the water, I actually had more oxygen than before I went under. It was a very miraculous experience. Not only that, but when I went into the water, I felt light. I thought I saw a light. I felt like I was in heaven. All of this reconfirmed the idea that I was going in the right direction. <br /><br />

